creator: MidDream Studios
descriptionHtml:
Battlefield of Ragnarok is a fast-paced 2D PvP online multiplayer action game set in the world of Vikings where medieval times blend with myths and legends.

As a fallen warrior you have joined your brave brothers and sisters in Valhalla.
It is not the end of your war times, though. For the final battle is yet to come!
Get ready, Einherjar, for Ragnarok, the Twilight of the Gods is coming!

FEATURES
⚔️ Online Multiplayer with Elements of RPG
You will fight the other Vikings in Valhalla in preparation for Ragnarok. Be warned: the competition is strong and fast. Get ready for a blood frenzy and go berserk yourself.

⚔️ Collect, Grow, and Fight!
Collect runes and grow in size to get an advantage over other Vikings or play with friends and challenge them with your score and skill.

⚔️ Wide Range of Weapons and Armors
You start from scratch as a pauper, but if you truly have the Viking spirit, you will soon get that shiny armor and mighty axe back again.

⚔️ Melee and Ranged
In this Viking game, you can choose your combat style and even combine various weapons such as swords, spears, axes, daggers, shields, and even ranged weapons such as bows, throwing knives, or stones.

⚔️ Status Effects
Battlefield of Ragnarok is an unforgiving place. During the battle, you will find refreshments such as mead, meat, and even mushrooms. They will give you a temporary bonus to power up your war spirits.

⚔️ Armour of Glory
Unlike many role-playing games, you will not be able to buy all the best equipment right away. To get the best bits, you must prove yourself worthy.

⚔️ Viking Warrior Customization
Choose from a set of different clothes, hair, and beard styles. Do it your way. Wanna wear a bikini without giving up that thick beard? No problem. Odin is the Allfather, not Somefather.

⚔️ Norse Art
Unlike other Viking games, BoR art was exclusively created by Raven from the North (Wardruna) and it draws from both historical findings and Norse mythology.

⚔️ Norse Music
Dark pagan ambient music by Nemuer will immerse you in the Old Norse atmosphere.

Download this multiplayer online game to experience the world of Vikings at its fiercest!


🛡️ PLEASE NOTE

Battlefield of Ragnarok is free to download and play, however, some game items can also be purchased for real money. If you do not want to use this feature, please set up password protection for purchases in the settings of your Google Play Store app.


🪓 CONTACT US

We value your feedback and want to make the game as best as possible!
Feel free to join our Discord server https://discord.gg/8wVrw7Kwvt for any kind of communication.

https://www.middreamstudios.com/bor/
https://www.instagram.com/theravenfromthenorth/ (ART)
https://www.youtube.com/c/NemuerMusic (MUSIC)
